1
00:00:01,980 --> 00:00:08,990
前情提要

2
00:00:03,410 --> 00:00:04,630
丘吉尔阁下
Mr Churchill...

3
00:00:04,630 --> 00:00:07,060
如果真要弄死一些人
If there are bodies to be buried,

4
00:00:07,320 --> 00:00:10,430
就挖洞深埋起来  要干净利落
dig holes and dig them deep.

5
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:12,000
别当着我妻儿的面抓我
Don't do this in here.

6
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:13,670
你们要将我从儿子面前带走吗
You're taking me away from my baby!

7
00:00:13,670 --> 00:00:15,330
-弗莱迪  -艾达
- Freddie! - Ada!

8
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:19,110
出卖弗莱迪·索恩的人不是我
It wasn't me who shopped Freddie Thorne.

9
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:21,660
他信任我  我告诉过你这一点
He trusts me. I told you that.

10
00:00:21,930 --> 00:00:23,660
我想我知道枪藏在哪里了
I think I know where the guns are hidden.

11
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:27,610
我要你保证  如果枪找到了
I want your word that Thomas Shelby will not be harmed

12
00:00:27,610 --> 00:00:29,100
你不能伤害汤玛斯·谢尔比
if the guns are recovered.

13
00:00:31,930 --> 00:00:35,050
如果能跟你合作真的很荣幸  肯波先生
It would be an honour to work with you, Mr Kimber.

14
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:38,970
没人可以跟我合作  都只能在我手下工作
Nobody works with me. People work for me.

15
00:00:40,210 --> 00:00:42,600
一颗黑星  这是什么意思
A black star? What does that mean?

16
00:00:42,970 --> 00:00:44,200
标上黑星那天
The black star day

17
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:47,050
是我们除掉比利·肯波和他的手下的日子
is the day we take out Billy Kimber and his men.

18
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:51,670
格蕾丝  你愿意嫁给我吗
Grace...will you marry me?

19
00:00:52,740 --> 00:00:54,160
你可以找到比我更好的
You deserve better.

20
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:55,790
是因为他吗
Is it him?!

21
00:00:56,780 --> 00:00:58,620
-他在哪儿  -他走了
- Where is he? - He left.

22
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,350
和酒吧女招待一起
With the barmaid.

23
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,170
服务生
Service.

24
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:33,630
我们两小时后才营业  你晚点再过来
We don't open two more hours. You come back later.

25
00:02:34,710 --> 00:02:35,780
警察
Police.

26
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,750
您是坎贝尔督察啊  先生
Inspector Campbell, sir.

27
00:02:44,550 --> 00:02:45,900
我们有什么麻烦了吗
Any trouble, sir?

28
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,070
听着
Look...

29
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,430
我知道
I know.

30
00:02:51,490 --> 00:02:53,090
我知道的
I know.

31
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:59,070
就是  我手下的好几个警官告诉我
That is, I am given to understand by several of my officers...

32
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:04,690
我手下的好几名警官说  很多人到这里来
several of my officers, that people come here...

33
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:09,030
男人会到这里来
That men come here for...

34
00:03:09,730 --> 00:03:11,770
寻求某种慰藉
a certain purpose.

35
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,850
亚瑟  亚瑟  醒醒
Arthur? Arthur, wake up.

36
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:30,980
回家去  洗个澡
Get home, get bathed.

37
00:03:31,010 --> 00:03:33,160
检查一下装备和武器
Check your kit, check your weapons.

38
00:03:36,070 --> 00:03:37,150
为什么
Why?

39
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,640
出什么事了
What's going on?

40
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,060
我们今天就要开干了
We're doing it today.

41
00:03:57,060 --> 00:03:58,870
准备好马车  查理
Fetch the wagons, Charlie.

42
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,780
就今天了
It's today.

43
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:26,490
爸爸  凯蒂又在床上撒尿了
Dad? Our Katie's done a wee in the bed again.

44
00:04:27,230 --> 00:04:29,050
我马上就来处理  小家伙
I'll be there in a minute, mate.

45
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,120
约翰  我告诉过你要记得锁门
John, I've told you to keep the doors locked.

46
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,480
冲进来的可能是任何人
It could've been anyone.

47
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:37,160
穿上衣服
Get dressed.

48
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,570
我们今天就开干了
We're doing it today.

49
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:40,630
事实上  他今天的任务就是干我
As a matter of fact, he's doing me today.

50
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:42,310
务必让他在9点前干完你
Make sure he's done you by nine.

51
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,410
你该学会敲门
You should learn to knock!

52
00:04:43,410 --> 00:04:45,030
今天不是敲门的日子
It's not a day for knocking.

53
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:50,250
上帝啊  一定要让今天顺利度过
Dear Lord, make this day pass well.

54
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,340
不要让任何人受伤
Let none get hurt

55
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,490
即使有人受伤  也不要是谢尔比家族的人
and make them that do not Shelbys.

56
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,320
照看好约翰
Watch John,

57
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:02,140
有好几个孩子依靠着他
cos he has so many depending on him.

58
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:04,710
照看好亚瑟
Watch Arthur

59
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:08,990
因为除了别人会伤害他  他也会伤害自己
because he's as likely to hurt himself as anyone else.

60
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,820
照看好汤玛斯
Watch Thomas.

61
00:05:13,100 --> 00:05:14,930
我知道他是什么样的人
I know how he is.

62
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:17,970
但他做出那些事都是为了我们
But he does what he does for us.

63
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:21,330
我觉得是
I think.

64
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,730
阿门
Amen.

65
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:32,650
我在战时每天早晨都祈祷
I used to do that every morning during the war.

66
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:35,080
我曾希望我可以最后一次祈祷就完事了
I hoped I'd done it for the last time.

67
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:37,500
今天就是你最后一次祈祷了  波莉
Today will be the last time, Poll.

68
00:05:39,030 --> 00:05:41,960
过了今天  就没必要再祈祷了
After today, there'll be no need for prayers.

69
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:43,780
我们就安定了
We'll be set.

70
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:48,140
十点半  家族会议
Family meeting, half ten.

71
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:51,670
浴   血

72
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:51,670
黑   帮

73
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:51,670
第一季终   『人人影视英剧社倾情奉献』   第六集

74
00:06:02,050 --> 00:06:05,400
我很抱歉让您久等了  现在真的很早
I'm sorry I kept you. It is so early.

75
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:08,360
是的  我...
Yes. I-I...

76
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:10,370
我昨晚一直没睡
I didn't sleep last night.

77
00:06:12,930 --> 00:06:16,850
张先生说你是个很特殊很特殊的客人
Mr Zhang said you are special, special customer.

78
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:29,970
你想坐下吗
Do you want to sit?

79
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:40,710
你想脱掉靴子吗
Do you want to take off your boots?

80
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,730
是的
Yes.

81
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:54,870
还有  这个
And...this.

82
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:02,060
系得好紧啊
So tight.

83
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:17,960
我们欢好时  可以让人帮你把衣服洗干净熨烫下
We can also clean and press your shirt while we do this.

84
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:20,820
你们的服务效率可真高
That's a very efficient service.

85
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:25,730
你以前从没来过这种地方吗
You never been to a place like this before?

86
00:07:27,670 --> 00:07:29,240
没关系的
It's OK.

87
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:32,820
有时候那些失去妻子的老男人也会到这里来
Sometimes old men who have lost their wives, they come here...

88
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:34,400
经常来的
all the time.

89
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:36,090
老男人
Old men?

90
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,550
我有那么老吗
I am so old?

91
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:41,140
不  我是说我很年轻
No! I mean I am young.

92
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,810
总之
Anyway...

93
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:46,660
我会让你也觉得恢复年轻状态的
I'll make you young as well.

94
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:48,550
婊子
Whore.

95
00:09:01,470 --> 00:09:03,050
亲爱的格蕾丝
'Dear Grace.

96
00:09:03,820 --> 00:09:07,060
我怀着沉重的心情给你写这封信
'I write this letter to you with a heavy heart.

97
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:11,770
我清楚地知道你干了什么  和谁一起干的
'I know exactly what you did, and with whom.

98
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:15,620
我在报告中一字都不会提的
'I will not mention any of it in my report.

99
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:17,670
但是  你必须明白
'However, you should be aware

100
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:23,180
我知道你已献身于我们不共戴天的仇敌
that I know you gave yourself to the man who is our sworn enemy.

101
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,400
那不仅是通敌行为
'That is not only treason,

102
00:09:26,650 --> 00:09:29,800
更是恶心至极的行为
'it is disgusting beyond all measure.

103
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,530
你父亲一定会以你为耻的
'Your father would be ashamed of you.

104
00:09:32,570 --> 00:09:36,310
至于我自己  我心痛不已
'And as for myself... I am beyond desolation.

105
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,880
你已经背叛了你生来就享有的
'You have betrayed every principle

106
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:42,280
一切荣耀和遵从的原则
'and standard of honour that was your birthright.

107
00:09:43,290 --> 00:09:45,250
你又是为了什么呢
'And for what?'

108
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:48,160
爱
Love.

109
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:12,710
天啊  我很抱歉  那是我弄的吗
Oh, my God, I'm sorry. Did I do that?

110
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:17,030
没关系  你是位很特殊很特殊的客人
It's OK. You are special, special customer.

111
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:20,150
你能陪我坐一会儿吗
Would you sit with me for a moment?

112
00:10:20,190 --> 00:10:21,830
求你了
Please.

113
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:57,060
衣服的钱
For the suits.

114
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,860
要听点有意思的消息吗
You want to hear something funny?

115
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:14,380
坎贝尔跟我的一个姑娘在里间
Campbell was in the back room with one of my girls.

116
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:28,220
我没带武器
I am unarmed.

117
00:11:32,580 --> 00:11:34,760
真奇怪啊  督察
It's curious, Inspector.

118
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:37,510
我以为你是来清理这座城市的
I thought you came here to clean up the city.

119
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:40,010
而不是来跟妓女上床的
Not to sleep with its whores.

120
00:11:41,930 --> 00:11:45,690
你跟之前来的警察没两样
You're no different from any other copper that came before you.

121
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:49,840
我和那些在我走后来接替我的人也没两样
I'm no different from those who would follow should I choose to leave.

122
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:51,890
你没理由留下
You've no reason to stay.

123
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:53,860
你的目的已经达到了
You have what you came for.

124
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,970
是的  我的目的达到了
Yes. I have what I came for.

125
00:11:57,370 --> 00:12:00,790
我中午要和温斯顿·丘吉尔先生开会
I have a meeting with Mr Winston Churchill at midday.

126
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,000
无疑他会恭喜我
And no doubt he intends to congratulate me

127
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,170
寻回了那些被盗的枪支
on finding those stolen guns.

128
00:12:06,900 --> 00:12:10,860
你还是不知道我们是怎么找到的  对吧
And you still don't know how we found them, do you?

129
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:12,770
很好
Good.

130
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:14,680
你走狗屎运罢了
Oh, you got lucky.

131
00:12:14,730 --> 00:12:16,080
是吗
Did I?

132
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,280
是的
Yeah.

133
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:20,590
我学到的一件事
One thing I have learned...

134
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:27,080
就是你我既对立  又统一
is that you and I are opposites, but also just the same.

135
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,840
就好像镜中像
Like an image in a mirror.

136
00:12:33,370 --> 00:12:36,270
我们讨厌别人
We hate people.

137
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:41,340
别人也讨厌我们
And they in turn hate us.

138
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:43,770
惧怕我们
And fear us.

139
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:52,850
今天  你会心碎
Before the day is over, your heart will be broken...

140
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,350
正如我一样
just the same as mine.

141
00:12:58,810 --> 00:13:01,190
像我们这样的人  谢尔比先生
Men like us, Mr Shelby...

142
00:13:02,230 --> 00:13:04,160
注定永远孤独
will always be alone.

143
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:07,620
我们得到的爱
And what love we get...

144
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,970
都必须付出代价
we will have to pay for.

145
00:13:11,970 --> 00:13:14,980
你忘了  督察
You forget, Inspector.

146
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:18,130
我有家人
I have my family.

147
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,820
祝你今天过得愉快
Enjoy your day.

148
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,500
小家伙
Oh, little one...

149
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:38,660
你比我更会跟他相处
You're much better with him than I am.

150
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:43,860
他这么快就安静下来是因为我身上没有奶味
He settles quicker with me cos he can't smell the milk.

151
00:13:43,870 --> 00:13:46,830
你累了  把他放回摇篮里吧
You're tired. Let's put him down.

152
00:13:52,050 --> 00:13:54,400
我家孩子特爱咬乳头
Mine were terrors for the tit.

153
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:56,420
两个都是
Both of them.

154
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,610
你不认识我的孩子们吧
Well, you never knew my children, did you?

155
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:01,980
不  我自己当时都还是个孩子
No, I was a child myself, then.

156
00:14:04,130 --> 00:14:06,110
你从没提起过
You never talk about them.

157
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,640
没理由说
Never had reason to.

158
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:14,690
一想到他们我就心疼
My heart breaks even when I think about them.

159
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:19,920
但今天
But today...

160
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:22,700
有理由了
I do have reason to.

161
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:24,830
坐下  艾达
Sit down, Ada.

162
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:35,790
他们一个三岁  一个五岁
They were three and five years old.

163
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:41,030
萨莉三岁  迈克尔五岁
Sally was three, Michael was five.

164
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:43,860
再过两周就六岁了
Two weeks away from being six.

165
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:49,870
那是周日早晨  我去教堂了
It was Sunday morning. I was at church.

166
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:54,910
"上帝不会原谅你"
"You're not forgiven."

167
00:14:55,910 --> 00:15:00,600
一个苦瓜脸贱人跟我说  "上帝不会原谅你"
This... pinch-faced bitch said to me, "You're not forgiven."

168
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:03,970
我洗完晾在外面的床单上
You see, some sheets I washed and hung on the line

169
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,000
印着一家酒店的名字
had the name of a hotel on them.

170
00:15:06,050 --> 00:15:07,630
那些床单在一件劫案中被偷
They'd been stolen in a robbery,

171
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:11,140
警方说酒店的服务员被人用短棍袭击了
and they said some porter at the hotel had been coshed.

172
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:14,880
附近有个女人把床单的事告诉了警方
And a woman from round here told the police about the sheets -

173
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:17,480
就是因为嫉妒我有新床单
jealous, you see, of the new sheets.

174
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:19,220
警察到来的时候
And when the police came,

175
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:25,080
发现一个用来制作杜松子酒的酒馏器
they found a spirit still for making a few drops of gin.

176
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:30,120
为此
And for that...

177
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:35,270
他们夺走了我的孩子们
They took my children from me.

178
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:40,120
也不告诉我将他们送去了哪
And they never told me where they took them.

179
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,550
他们这么做是因为他们有这个能力
And they did it cos they could.

180
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,230
因为我很软弱
And cos I was weak.

181
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:47,660
但他们绝不会夺走你的孩子
But they will never take your baby away from you.

182
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,560
知道为什么吗
Do you know why?

183
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:52,090
因为汤米不会让他们这么做
Cos Tommy wouldn't let them.

184
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:55,220
因为汤米不会让他们欺负我们
Cos Tommy won't let them walk all over us.

185
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:59,360
是汤米给了这个家族力量和权力
Now it is Tommy who has given strength and power to this family.

186
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:02,150
因为他知道
Cos he knows...

187
00:16:02,870 --> 00:16:06,280
