Think about them right now.

557
00:40:21,300 --> 00:40:25,760
还想斗就斗吧  但我不会移走这孩子的
And fight if you want to, but that baby ain't moving anywhere.

558
00:40:27,470 --> 00:40:28,940
我也不走
And neither am I.

559
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:35,490
她说得对
She's right, you know.

560
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:38,890
你们凭什么要死
Why should all you men die?

561
