把枪举起来
Hold your guns up!

567
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,520
够了
Enough.

568
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:15,120
这场战斗由肯波和我单挑
Kimber and me fought this battle one on one.

569
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:17,860
现在一切结束了
It's over.

570
00:41:23,850 --> 00:41:25,570
回去找你们的家人吧
Go home to your families.

571
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:59,750
斯卡德伯特  科利  把他抬起来
Scudboat, Curly...pick him up.

572
00:42:30,540 --> 00:42:34,000
我想问你一个问题  之后我就会离开
I want to ask you one question. Then I'll leave.

573
00:42:35,020 --> 00:42:38,480
汤米知道我是谁  你跟他说什么了
Tommy knows who I am. What did you say to him?

574
00:42:40,120 --> 00:42:41,830
你跟他说什么了
What did you say to him?

575
00:42:47,030 --> 00:42:48,090
我告诉他
I told him...

576
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:52,820
他会在明天之前心碎
..that his heart would be broken before the day was over.

577
00:42:55,650 --> 00:42:57,010
所以看来
So, it seems...

578
00:42:58,620 --> 00:43:00,860
你弄碎了两个人的心  格蕾丝
You've broken two hearts, Grace.

579
00:43:04,630 --> 00:43:05,850
我自己的心也碎了
As well as my own.

580
00:43:17,090 --> 00:43:18,900
坚持  汤米  坚持
That's it, Tommy, that's it.

581
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:20,390
坚持住  汤米
Bite it, Tommy.

582
00:43:20,830 --> 00:43:22,470
拿出来  快拿出来
Take it. Take it!

583
00:43:22,470 --> 00:43:24,470
-按住他  -坚持    
- Hold him still. - That's it, lad.

584
00:43:24,750 --> 00:43:26,790
加油  加油
Come on. Come on!

585
00:43:30,850 --> 00:43:33,130
取出来了  我还是宝刀未老
There! I still have the knack.

586
00:43:36,200 --> 00:43:37,190
喝一口
Have a drink.

587
00:43:41,640 --> 00:43:43,200
好  深呼吸
Right, deep breath.

588
00:43:44,670 --> 00:43:46,540
好了  结束了
That's it. It's done.

589
00:44:09,990 --> 00:44:11,710
现在可以好好把他葬在
Now we can bury him properly

590
00:44:12,370 --> 00:44:14,110
之前为他挖的坟墓里了
in the grave we dug for him.

591
00:44:18,030 --> 00:44:20,910
在高高的山坡上  他会喜欢的
It's high on a hill. He'll like that.

592
00:44:29,660 --> 00:44:31,750
-敬高速炮弹丹尼  -丹尼
- To Danny Whizz-Bang. - Danny.

593
00:44:31,750 --> 00:44:33,730
愿所有人都可以死两次
May we all die twice.

594
00:44:37,290 --> 00:44:38,610
敬高速炮弹丹尼
To Danny Whizz-Bang.

595
00:44:42,200 --> 00:44:43,450
高速炮弹丹尼
Danny Whizz-Bang.

596
00:45:03,040 --> 00:45:03,940
走吧
Come on.

597
00:45:04,610 --> 00:45:06,530
今天是我们的大好日子  去庆祝吧
The day is ours, let's celebrate.

598
00:45:30,390 --> 00:45:31,250
怎么样
Well?

599
00:45:32,610 --> 00:45:33,650
谁赢了
Who won?

600
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:39,770
找到了威廉·肯波被人枪杀的尸体
A Mr William Kimber has been found dead with a gunshot wound.

601
00:45:40,660 --> 00:45:44,960
所以我猜是剃刀党赢了
So, I'm guessing that means the Peaky Blinders won.

602
00:45:45,330 --> 00:45:46,220
长官
Sir.

603
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:52,070
另外  那个共党分子  弗莱迪·索恩
Also, the communist agitator Freddie Thorne

604
00:45:52,070 --> 00:45:55,510
在押运期间被人持枪劫走了
was taken from his transport by armed men.

605
00:45:56,830 --> 00:45:59,650
由于当时街上没有警察
Since there were no police officers on the street at the time...

606
00:45:59,710 --> 00:46:01,140
那完全是遵照您的命令
following your orders...

607
00:46:01,450 --> 00:46:04,430
他轻松逃掉了  现在逍遥法外
he managed to escape easily and is now at large.

608
00:46:05,550 --> 00:46:08,460
狱警说他认出了劫持他的人
The prison officers said they recognised the men.

609
00:46:08,460 --> 00:46:11,210
也是剃刀党的人  长官
They were Peaky Blinders as well, sir.

610
00:46:12,870 --> 00:46:15,330
我们可以去抓几个人来问问
I mean, we could go down there and make a few arrests

611
00:46:15,340 --> 00:46:17,760
但肯定问不出什么
but, er, no-one will have seen anything.

612
00:46:18,680 --> 00:46:21,370
而且因为没有其他警官做证人  所以
And there were no officers there to witness, so...

613
00:46:23,100 --> 00:46:25,490
谢尔比家的人连谋杀罪都可以逃掉了
The Shelbys will get away with murder.

614
00:46:26,500 --> 00:46:28,110
就像以前一样
Just like they always have.

615
00:46:29,810 --> 00:46:31,440
有些事是不会变的
Some things never change.

616
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:33,470
对吗  长官
Eh, sir?

617
00:46:58,980 --> 00:47:00,020
敬
A toast...

618
00:47:00,620 --> 00:47:03,330
敬谢尔比有限公司
A toast, to Shelby Limited!

619
00:47:03,330 --> 00:47:04,870
谢尔比
Shelby!

620
00:47:10,310 --> 00:47:13,050
他有几个儿子  我们该帮他们找个工作吗
He's got sons. Should we find work for them?

621
00:47:13,250 --> 00:47:14,740
不  让他们自由发展吧
No. Let them be.

622
00:47:15,570 --> 00:47:18,580
让他们找个普通的工作  做个普通的人
Let them find ordinary work like ordinary men.

623
00:48:03,460 --> 00:48:05,880
请帮我接丘吉尔先生
Could you put me through to Mr Churchill, please?

624
00:48:08,360 --> 00:48:09,280
长官
Yes, sir.

625
00:48:10,490 --> 00:48:11,370
长官
Sir...

626
00:48:12,620 --> 00:48:15,560
我为我的仕途做了一个决定
I have made a decision about my future.

627
00:48:30,360 --> 00:48:32,020
所有人都要走了
Everyone's leaving town.

628
00:48:33,620 --> 00:48:35,390
-汤米你受伤了  -我没事
- Tommy, you're hurt. - I'm fine.

629
00:48:38,240 --> 00:48:39,740
我该说什么
What exactly can I say?

630
00:48:39,740 --> 00:48:41,090
我不知道  格蕾丝
I don't know, Grace.

631
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,610
我可以告诉你我的真实身份
I could tell you who I really am.

632
00:48:46,240 --> 00:48:47,670
我觉得我已经知道了
I think I know who you are.

633
00:48:49,630 --> 00:48:50,930
你也知道我
And you know who I am.

634
00:48:50,970 --> 00:48:52,930
琐事细节并不重要
The circumstance is not important.

635
00:48:54,290 --> 00:48:56,580
-琐事细节  -仅此而已
- Circumstance? - Is all it is.

636
00:48:58,610 --> 00:48:59,840
那只是公事
Just uniform.

637
00:49:07,500 --> 00:49:09,900
总有一天我会把枪扔进大运河
Someday I will throw this gun in the canal.

638
00:49:10,890 --> 00:49:12,010
为什么现在不行
Why not now?

639
00:49:22,820 --> 00:49:24,330
但爱就是这么来了  汤米
Here it comes, Tommy.

640
00:49:27,240 --> 00:49:28,390
我爱你
I love you.

641
00:49:31,200 --> 00:49:33,780
也就这么散去了  格蕾丝
And there it goes, Grace.

642
00:49:35,350 --> 00:49:37,060
就这样散去
Away it goes.

643
00:49:38,590 --> 00:49:40,710
我们不管再说多少次
We can say it as much as we like...

644
00:49:43,210 --> 00:49:44,750
也是不可能的
But there's no chance.

645
00:49:58,070 --> 00:50:00,900
我会在伦敦呆一周  地址在这里
I'll be in London one week. This address.

646
00:50:01,570 --> 00:50:03,870
忙完这里的事然后来找我
Finish your business here and join me.

647
00:50:06,780 --> 00:50:08,060
我有个主意
I have an idea.

648
00:50:25,580 --> 00:50:28,010
-他来了  汤米  -要酒吗
- There he is... Tommy. - Drink?

649
00:50:33,620 --> 00:50:34,710
不要威士忌
Not whisky.

650
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:39,620
你看吧台后面
If you check behind the bar...

651
00:50:41,900 --> 00:50:44,230
有一瓶香槟
you will find a bottle of champagne.

652
00:50:54,590 --> 00:50:55,850
是她买的
The one she bought.

653
00:51:02,930 --> 00:51:04,430
今天是个好日子
Today was a good day.

654
00:51:08,760 --> 00:51:11,060
当肯波的人都聚在这里的时候
All of Kimber's men were busy here,

655
00:51:11,530 --> 00:51:15,000
李家的人抢到了所有乌斯特比赛的操控权
so the Lee boys took all the pitches at the Worcester races.

656
00:51:18,100 --> 00:51:20,140
简直比事先安排的还好
It couldn't have gone better if we'd planned it.

657
00:51:20,760 --> 00:51:22,540
谢尔比兄弟有限公司
Shelby Brothers Limited

658
00:51:23,070 --> 00:51:26,150
现在是这个国家
are now the third largest

659
00:51:26,250 --> 00:51:29,160
第三大的合法赌马公司
legal race track operation in the country.

660
00:51:29,160 --> 00:51:30,870
干杯  只有萨比利公司
Cheers! Only the Sabinis

661
00:51:30,870 --> 00:51:33,040
和所罗门公司在我们之上
and the Solomons are bigger than us, boys.

662
00:51:37,990 --> 00:51:40,440
我所有家人都在此庆祝
And all my family is here to celebrate.

663
00:51:44,990 --> 00:51:46,820
敬谢尔比兄弟有限公司
To Shelby Brothers Limited.

664
00:51:47,440 --> 00:51:49,060
谢尔比  兄弟
Shelby! Brothers!

665
00:51:49,060 --> 00:51:50,090
干杯
Cheers.

666
00:52:06,940 --> 00:52:08,150
还有其它人
There'll be others.

667
00:52:16,880 --> 00:52:18,000
敬其它人
To the others.

668
00:52:20,610 --> 00:52:21,540
所有人
All of them.

669
00:52:47,850 --> 00:52:49,850
谢尔比兄弟有限公司

670
00:52:54,030 --> 00:52:55,070
亲爱的格蕾丝
Dear Grace...

671
00:52:55,940 --> 00:52:58,510
没有了秘书  我只能亲手写这封信
Without a secretary, I write my own letters

672
00:52:58,920 --> 00:53:00,530
我对你毫无恨意
and I write without malice.

673
00:53:01,980 --> 00:53:04,230
我很久前就学会憎恨我的敌人
I learnt long ago to hate my enemies.

674
00:53:05,430 --> 00:53:07,190
却从没爱过任何人
But I've never loved one before.

675
00:53:12,510 --> 00:53:14,560
一起去纽约的主意很棒
The idea of New York is interesting

676
00:53:15,550 --> 00:53:19,190
但我为了今天的胜利  努力了很久
but I have worked so hard for this day, for this victory.

677
00:53:19,950 --> 00:53:21,700
我在这里肩负着重要责任
I have responsibilities here

678
00:53:22,560 --> 00:53:26,620
要去保护那些需要保护的人  和我爱的人
for people I need to protect and people who I love.

679
00:53:29,590 --> 00:53:32,900
战争之前  当我需要做重大决定的时候
Before the war, when I had an important decision to make,

680
00:53:33,020 --> 00:53:34,430
我喜欢扔硬币
I used to flip a coin.

681
00:53:35,200 --> 00:53:36,950
也许这次也要这样决定了
Perhaps that is what I will do again.

682
00:53:40,090 --> 00:53:42,230
波莉告诉我  你是真的爱上我了
Polly tells me you fell in love for real

683
00:53:42,440 --> 00:53:44,960
她对这种事的直觉向来都是准的
and Polly is never wrong about matters of the heart.

684
00:53:48,960 --> 00:53:51,500
我会在三天内告诉你我的决定
I will give you my decision within three days.

685
00:53:54,690 --> 00:53:57,440
爱你的  汤玛斯·谢尔比
